'''Grayweave''' was a low-cost food created by single-cell organisms inside a [[grayweave generator]]. Developed to feed the poor, it resembled thick gray felt and did not taste appetizing, but the food did provide enough nutritional value to sustain a [[Human/Legends|Human]].<ref name="Rebel Stand">''[[The New Jedi Order: Enemy Lines II: Rebel Stand]]''</ref> When [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] [[Battle of Coruscant (Yuuzhan Vong War)|fell]] to the [[Yuuzhan Vong]], the [[Coruscanti/Legends|Coruscanti]] who were left behind were forced to subsist on grayweave for their continued sustenance.<ref name="The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref> Many offworld citizens felt it was a horrible fate for the residents of the former [[The galaxy/Legends|galactic]] [[Capital/Legends|capital]].<ref name="Rebel Stand" />

